Our family lawyers in Montevideo know this can be a difficult thing to come to terms with, which is why we work tirelessly to help give women the representation and equal rights they deserve.

Our Services

Our matrimonial legal practice focuses on the following areas:

Divorces in Uruguay

Divorce cases are often very challenging for many people. Not only does the pain of a break-down in communication and trust need to be overcome, but also the fear of what may or may not come next for custodial rights and visitation.

As one of the top family law practices in Uruguay (Law Firm Monte), our 40+ years of family law experience in Uruguay is something that we are truly proud of.

We offer assistance in the areas of:

Legal Separation

Annulment of marriage

Restoration of full marriage

Property post separation

Void marriages

Unjustified divorce

Succession in divorced cases

Nationality or citizenship cases

We assist with the filling of court papers, testimonies, case advocacy, and providing second opinion in the time of need.
